Class Feature

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.giscore.events.AbstractObject

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, IGISObject, VisitableGeometry, IDataSerializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
NetworkLink, Overlay
public class Feature extends Common
We've seen the start of a feature set. The start of the feature set has all the available information about the feature. After the start of a feature, there will be zero or more geometry objects seen.

DRAND
